mil.nga.giat.geowave.accumulo.metadata

Class AccumuloIndexStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • mil.nga.giat.geowave.accumulo.metadata.AbstractAccumuloPersistence<Index>
      • mil.nga.giat.geowave.accumulo.metadata.AccumuloIndexStore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IndexStore

    public class AccumuloIndexStore
extends AbstractAccumuloPersistence<Index>
implements IndexStore
    This class will persist Index objects within an Accumulo table for GeoWave metadata. The indices will be persisted in an "INDEX" column family. There is an LRU cache associated with it so staying in sync with external updates is not practical - it assumes the objects are not updated often or at all. The objects are stored in their own table.
